{"tid":1198581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（有片）其實警察既態度係咪真係有需要去到一個爛仔既程度？（請廣傳）","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T10:32:13.000Z","uid":207077,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"79c56684a21bcea526d4525f9609bb5029b1cf8b","tid":1198581,"uid":207077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QWz6ApW1eVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQWz6ApW1eVE&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=3a3b1715\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QWz6ApW1eVE</a><br />\n我姑且當你收到上頭order，你地係圍住人地幾粒鐘唔比人走既舉動係無可避免。但係當你抄底曬人地資料，放人走既時候，真係有必要當住一眾記者，用爛仔般既態度去對班手無寸鐵，為緊你發聲既學生，義士？ 人地好好地向你解釋緊，你根本完全聽唔入耳。去到最後你仲要兇個學生：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">『你唔好在係度出現，我認得你啊。』</span></span> （大概意思係咁，現場收音環境太差，大家可以開聲聽下） 呢條片可能只係<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">冰山一角</span></span>，對黑警黎講只係日常生活，雞毛蒜皮之事。幸好有立場新聞既記者朋友全程影住你地，如果唔係情況更加不堪設想。<br />\n唔好再同我講話你身不由己，身在曹營心在漢。呢種對人既態度係你地每一位警察自己選擇。可能通過修例之後，我發佈呢條影片已經係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">煽動緊國家安全</span></span>，畢竟無人清楚港共對<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">犯罪</span></span>既定義係D乜。但係好希望各位巴打絲打如果識呢位盡忠職守既好警察的話，可以比呢條片佢地既親朋戚友，睇下佢<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">6月10日既</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英勇事蹟</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n各位，如果你地仲目擊到黑警有任何不合理既舉動的話，希望你地都可以一齊發聲，算係略盡綿力，對自己有個交代。"},{"pid":"02653d953396a1bcf77a3d2bb2988b26ed17ec0e","tid":1198581,"uid":207077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"自推一個先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786a3c4c3b208a90a1d9557bf3364b3da1ae0752","tid":1198581,"uid":207077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:30:04.000Z","msg":"希望比更加多人睇到，幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b30b144ce7fc2c3558112b455929feda4263cad","tid":1198581,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0298f5012551371642bc6c6888063b9e6625a4d7","tid":1198581,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:31:27.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話係有牌爛仔"},{"pid":"acaaf3e0d9801befe0356ecf12d4d2255d7cb5bd","tid":1198581,"uid":207077,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bd9TYNd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbd9TYNd.png&h=cdcd3eef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKWONFz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKWONFz.png&h=b0968c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可能你本身已經係爛仔啦"},{"pid":"48e83b80a0dea50f6658af4807b083388826eea3","tid":1198581,"uid":104833,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"不嬲中學操行最差班Mk仔先去考毅進當差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e963c291436e1b7e6cc3ac6a85462078528d7f07","tid":1198581,"uid":231040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:36:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5780de590a51d990cf663104a613940e984be9fd","tid":1198581,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67aa5de00d4bc41f8e53deb2086a4950966d4f49","tid":1198581,"uid":38745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:54:12